{"tid":2156484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"live許智峯被跟蹤：狗唔會搜車、唔會透露人身份、會放司機走","createTime":"2020-08-14T12:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T14:04:50.000Z","uid":318505,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"db48fbfc94448c390cdd0c9588e207e032bade40","tid":2156484,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"狗：因為車入面係自稱記者 所以放<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/409841406641559/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffans.hkgolden%2Fvideos%2F409841406641559%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcdHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=34ce73d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/409841406641559/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">好大嘅官威啊</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次各位記者行家識做啦"},{"pid":"3df2199fece7aab97e09790894e40808bd2a0f5c","tid":2156484,"uid":64522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"From TG<br />\n許智峯疑似被兩隻國安跟蹤 許智峯發現後上前質問二人 驚甴其後到場啲問二人拎身份証 有街坊目睹其中一人隊咗張黃色memo俾其中一個藍衫 藍衫馬上收落袋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10157104552675286/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fwesterndistrict%2Fpermalink%2F10157104552675286%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcdHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=7d9239a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10157104552675286/</a>"},{"pid":"9cc715792346a3a9fdf36a11df75fd6cfb572d25","tid":2156484,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:55:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9a186fb8bd0c5400ca2de37bf6d2ad2498fc2ef2","tid":2156484,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"最新：車已放、狗撲許智峯、許有受傷"},{"pid":"9812c3b351db959f956bdf3c5ccaf4cb25e49d8b","tid":2156484,"uid":318505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8QNLJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8QNLJ8.jpg&h=90bdf806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港多名民主派人士本月表示懷疑被人跟隨，其中民主黨立法會議員許智峯今日（14日）晚上 7 時許懷疑被一架黑色私家車跟蹤。許智峯之後報警，並在堅尼地城科士街與私家車司機及乘客對質，發現對方持有攝錄機、相機等器材。許智峯在 Facebook 指，該車輛被揭發後欲即時逃走，車身更撞到他，沒有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後接報到場，車上兩名人士聲稱自己是記者，現場人士發現其車尾箱有土木工程署承辦商的標誌牌。直至 8 時許，共約 20 名警員到場，並手持圓盾戒備，及用封鎖線包圍現場，要求記者到另一邊拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n有警員指事件是一宗交通意外，隨即引起現場市民不滿。"},{"pid":"e38e62f0b15d4580819bc382cef85237bb56852c","tid":2156484,"uid":321059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3df2199fece7aab97e09790894e40808bd2a0f5c","tid":2156484,"uid":64522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"From TG<br />\n許智峯疑似被兩隻國安跟蹤 許智峯發現後上前質問二人 驚甴其後到場啲問二人拎身份証 有街坊目睹其中一人隊咗張黃色memo俾其中一個藍衫 藍衫馬上收落袋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10157104552675286/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fwesterndistrict%2Fpermalink%2F10157104552675286%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcdHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=7d9239a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10157104552675286/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"涉嫌老妨喎<br />\n雖然黑警今時今日會咁做絕育唔出奇"},{"pid":"886b704292dd8a4dff790656ed7edd1efbdb0e96","tid":2156484,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人比人偷車/認得車上面係咩自己屋企人啊"},{"pid":"eeb5b2bce4af87dd2b6267707b761284d7606265","tid":2156484,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T13:06:09.000Z","msg":"放twitter link算啦"},{"pid":"9d8eb0576ac30d7d9f561f4c282651144d3af262","tid":2156484,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08